
Compiled on Ubuntu 16.04, should run on later Ubuntu releases also.

Add the "lib" subdir to your $LD_LIBRARY_PATH, then "bv" should run fine.

eg:

tar xvf bsonview-0.0.1b.tar.xz
cd bsonview-0.0.1b
export LD_LIBRARY_PATH="$PWD/lib:$LD_LIBRARY_PATH"
./bv huge.bson

Source is available at https://github.com/devkev/bsonview

